{"tid":2493724,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(初次獨遊記)6日5夜福岡小倉之旅","createTime":"2021-04-18T06:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T13:53:28.000Z","uid":116706,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ad14f80f5dd2a06b985f4c7dae1743c79ee62dde","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:34:53.000Z","msg":"呢排睇旅遊台, 見到經過呢一年時間武肺搞到冇得去旅行而令到遊記數目越嚟越少, 啱啱碌返之前第一次獨遊嘅相, 就心血來潮試下寫小弟第一篇遊記<br />\n(文筆唔好請諒解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n睇開旅遊台同blog, 見到其他人獨遊經歷好似好正, 無拘無束咁, 所以一路以嚟都好想試下. 喺2018年中, 由於我攞咗年尾一個禮拜大假, 所以就諗住嚟一次獨遊<br />\n<br />\n地點方面諗咗一陣, 由於之前旅遊經驗好少, 只係細個同屋企人去過大陸同台灣. 第一次去都係去返啲大路嘅日韓台泰算. 韓國一條仔去冇嘢好做, 台灣就去過. 日本泰國中間揀, 最後揀咗去好多香港人嘅鄉下-日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用咗幾個月時間做research睇blog, 最後終於喺2018年10月尾出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmenRb5R6FTKYedpPbABYAa45SyaS7hxySDrTZpLSv9avr?filename=JRmXGBz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRmXGBz.png&h=1769f811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW3E1overQdaNQw8Z313fWDxiwAsytBJJmsVWT1WsC6Nc?filename=sP4uxJQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsP4uxJQ.png&h=1853514e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQyJfn9GMK9ipZxvb2qLtfdFS8jB4K5z4VzJkYEqWHk1W?filename=AcsG8ha.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAcsG8ha.png&h=6bd502ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay1-2: 福岡巿內<br />\nDay3: 太宰府<br />\nDay4: 糸島<br />\nDay5: 門司港+下關<br />\nDay6: 小倉<br />\n<br />\n行程方面, 由於唔好行街, 所以主要都係睇景點. 洗費方面成程好似用咗4千蚊左右<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去住啲相先 (陳年舊手機影, 有啲會矇)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaxzfeCLj2NoshV7jHB5VeBzGNmfCNfBGfxHP8wqgWf3G?filename=YFfhGL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYFfhGL4.jpg&h=a9b4c1ab&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS3J1HFG1buD38a61JJGwEnNRdkssQGi63pa5jibvvU38?filename=ZuDftqY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZuDftqY.jpg&h=de4ea024&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPpDs6bTk5rwLzbfhdR9JsHnaVFy5L5AonLzkZkxoV83s?filename=a1b46cJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa1b46cJ.jpg&h=7a07b51f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVof2sSvRci9ycNTdZ14hUSeiiQmxThGfAjDzFDWSavSp?filename=2qyOOq0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qyOOq0.jpg&h=89931f4a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeJ5mZz51Jvg4AJ6k2FeKrqGorYvuuqPJnaV87CLUzNZi?filename=gmObMcJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgmObMcJ.jpg&h=09c9c33d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY7Kakamz3Uh5Kxc3SaQQRHgFRXBk7awivJTRL7PMRKYj?filename=BnV5QEo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnV5QEo.jpg&h=401f50f1&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV7HgaLHB2vXZV1X9PKcVT6YS3kwhWqo8vnL9nPQk9zM4?filename=zVdK6cK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzVdK6cK.jpg&h=6e406dd3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZK65F5pBQVkBGFnSWdUui1CNXFYhey49RZhjZZ6jw1AN?filename=fRX4mL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRX4mL4.jpg&h=f78bc445&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmchbVB9NPot3Bh4TZCJdNLeyW6UYhJWyP6rqmF2R3NSZJ?filename=w7pircH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7pircH.jpg&h=c2ef5eff&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR6RkLNpb8Pc8EdR239zLQuUjw3NzMc5ED32f4j5Zp1nQ?filename=XgERMcK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXgERMcK.jpg&h=c023f6ba&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNUvPymQAduXqZzdPe1H7WPou2DgAts6ujbqMoSZE8YAR?filename=aZgkExG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZgkExG.jpg&h=483679f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXNEgJQ1ubHWAkG8Jw9mBe6pMQTcDbBpZ3kMunsDe6Jq5?filename=BxQdZxF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxQdZxF.jpg&h=58f26792&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSSVw7SMJBUNqKicM9Fw61jsdApoC22dJrX57DzH26fwi?filename=u8HoCjo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu8HoCjo.jpg&h=2640f1cc&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRHWdM9gbRcDW2qpKgL3eJi8Aenuo8Eaw3FDE9JCa695h?filename=K6RgXjp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK6RgXjp.jpg&h=9ad25108&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTCqdtbFtRPGaiejftX6b1j9p8Jis4dwLRetJ6HAJ6QKP?filename=LDB8Oq4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDB8Oq4.jpg&h=84d97c33&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNb2woqC3LNofP1d4RBrvoa7Rgrr53zyjb5SKrzCzixLa?filename=kptnSSJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkptnSSJ.jpg&h=a8e0e5f0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVQts91U53SxLa9HHWcwHXAMuNVUnNLhrhWSEbaWwsDPN?filename=hbXsjxz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbXsjxz.jpg&h=690c2afe&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVHShX4s3Yg9Hd6ZqgPCHqkYAFkpPhv1JH1wAKqB49EBu?filename=EAzKmL1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAzKmL1.jpg&h=9e73be64&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後不定時出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f4c1a7d1380686d92ccc26b98b021c14d6f2fc","tid":2493724,"uid":292601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:38:42.000Z","msg":"正 我都係同你差唔多<br />\n2015左右獨遊北九州<br />\n自始愛上左呢個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但應該再無機會獨遊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea24d71136a42b5e02f459a9e1b07d97caaaca6","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:24:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span class=\"x-large\">Day 1</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n飛機就搭UO, 早機去下午機返連稅1128. 呢個時間我又覺得OK喎. 再平啲時間又太閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nUO600 0735HKG-&gt;1200FUK<br />\n搭通宵機場巴士去機場, 5點幾去到. 用張已成歷史嘅AE CX elite入公廁lounge食咗個魚蛋粉坐多一陣就上機<br />\n<br />\n瞓咗陣就到福岡. 福岡機場嘅好處就係近巿區, 搭地鐵幾個字就到博多駅.<br />\n拿拿臨拖住篋去食嘢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUgjV44ZTJx9MZMM18Wbex17GTBL28RAo1Vx3HWTr2S6T?filename=AtgMAeC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtgMAeC.jpg&h=72cd0859&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一雙見都多人推介, 喺博多駅行幾分鐘就到<br />\n去到見到有條廿幾人嘅人龍, 好似全部都係日本人? 之前聽講話去有人龍嘅鋪頭實無死<br />\n望一望入面得10幾個位, 結果由12點幾等咗個幾鐘去到兩點先入到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQKqhTAZyo6EYUh68xVN55bK9eBQLdGgotrTwBh1Pwgne?filename=BEMTZJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBEMTZJM.jpg&h=6472f5a0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n佢賣點係濃豬骨湯, 喺門口排緊隊嘅時候已經聞到一大浸其實有啲臭嘅味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似有啲生豬嘅腥味, 心諗今次可能伏咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但見到咁多人排隊, 就抱住一試無妨嘅心態試下<br />\n啊, 食落口又幾好味喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完拉麪就返酒店, 食飽飽最啱就行路<br />\n所以就拖住篋由博多行去天神南嘅酒店擺低行李先, 行到去啱啱夠鐘check in<br />\n今次book咗喺天神南嘅Benikea Calton Hotel Fukuoka Tenjin, 4晚唔使1200蚊, 好抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmajbnPNDU3VQKfZYW8HsTFXK6Lzjd4mbrJTMCbA7tsodC?filename=dZPFENy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZPFENy.jpg&h=2c40f2d7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXyyf6xseaT6MHQJqGP7xyQk34rroFxKM38yH86km8tPF?filename=dhDOOHy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdhDOOHy.jpg&h=5b0eabf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYTUXiY44ojUZjS9Qe8Sn1KHcDUycsgCFhXjLWnwLsq3r?filename=A6RAtHC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6RAtHC.jpg&h=d4e8d3e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmbi3KB5g3rxFZWYNyF78dWZ5CoMRfNkPTVkAZ59C566HB?filename=XvqtOH6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvqtOH6.jpg&h=e3b08908&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n第一次用免治馬桶, 感覺好奇妙, 好正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>待續</ins></strong>"},{"pid":"60923dbba32cd72237de0a3a8f05f7b3a572acdc","tid":2493724,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:25:36.000Z","msg":"牛腸鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23be1f4e7d39b24ebfc10f0b37f685261967312f","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:18:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span class=\"x-large\">Day 1 (cont.)</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n擺低行李就拿拿臨出去. 由於Day1-2都喺福岡巿內, 而福岡地鐵又貫穿咗巿區好多景點, 所以喺福岡機場時就買咗地鐵2 day pass, 機場出巿區嗰程就用得 <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmchvWcA4FLmkaZUMQdPX3PM694WsSayYffxknygThzSPj?filename=Vy2sjUy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVy2sjUy.jpg&h=65dbc4cd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n酒店行5分鐘就到地鐵站, 第一站筥崎宮<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ6N7XBR4fEk8CK4raVrTCkeAPQ4Cs67gW83rgVF8hasf?filename=E5pRMA8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE5pRMA8.jpg&h=7aef45f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdBiGZm926EdiiW61Dymz8cK5Ysf3oevhVDzHbbXRDgsB?filename=Sc2gdf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSc2gdf8.jpg&h=9d4dd3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaxzfeCLj2NoshV7jHB5VeBzGNmfCNfBGfxHP8wqgWf3G?filename=VKssjV8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVKssjV8.jpg&h=75829980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfBHnxNgRazuqJYbwsKF8F4NYQzHNjJ2DSaUg5jNXw8Tp?filename=MO5xv23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMO5xv23.jpg&h=01b9cc5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTq2sWwhAL55cGkV5oxiMn6drTxCazTNhi9niR2c398kK?filename=x0v18PK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx0v18PK.jpg&h=d4e3194d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後搭返嚟東長寺, 櫛田神社<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZpptevA9RF1RZDVFVHd7e4Rf88fNc7wWFJtFUhVeQjxk?filename=wQqNjXz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQqNjXz.jpg&h=070e4654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n解鎖subway pass背景<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdADUmks1dSvhxkg2vgYYNwn3uZtVC4uxnYEidKF1cfLh?filename=sdOyZZg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsdOyZZg.jpg&h=5906a2b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUydf5cwXWKxsN639hruHpeAYWNE4JScEVrcVSLewMp2Y?filename=8hVNjZg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8hVNjZg.jpg&h=352edc9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS3J1HFG1buD38a61JJGwEnNRdkssQGi63pa5jibvvU38?filename=ijRwMEe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FijRwMEe.jpg&h=238a9fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf15mjtzHNyz58iMEu4uef8Lpud7jyLsf2LykZTnERYzk?filename=iD1dfxA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiD1dfxA.jpg&h=173577d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWzVqv8SkqGxsCqrj3zjT9AyQ8w6MvmVeF3jJWWXJGsGz?filename=5vmMAxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5vmMAxB.jpg&h=9a40cc95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWSnhWczsQGKDnLZHLZKEgGZ7bqC4gKatZPcWBxKxBpKe?filename=KXkhHcA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKXkhHcA.jpg&h=b6d51be5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW8x2qwH1jbWKHMiV4ZgbqZp7L7PYPBDpnM915TZirAAo?filename=VSap6Eg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVSap6Eg.jpg&h=5824004d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP8XanzLE9HqCdCyiXSbmV4XLTJt29RNAdjjh1sT1jksC?filename=8DvmpqW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8DvmpqW.jpg&h=ae40429d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYo8i3jrH7uGFsddRKdYrPuNrZriaRkuELsg3jQCXtW86?filename=eu2WXLW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feu2WXLW.jpg&h=9e0a3647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到隻牛畀人摸到令哂, 我又摸一摸先<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSqTpsbQmBJLrYAfUzRkiSBJYpnXzNmmFSxLfmn26UycC?filename=M89eKr7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM89eKr7.jpg&h=618376bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日覺得日本文化源遠流長, 啲神社好值得去. 雖然好似間間差唔多, 但係入到去成個環境會令你心靈即刻洗滌咗, 舒服哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多本地人都會入去誠心參拜<br />\n<br />\n行到差唔多, 過隔離5分鐘路程嘅博多運河城行下<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmbh4qFGdU2ekndi55e3vT7YYN1DpBQz4C8CmRRz7K4wPG?filename=BmDWdnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmDWdnV.jpg&h=01b27df1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPpDs6bTk5rwLzbfhdR9JsHnaVFy5L5AonLzkZkxoV83s?filename=zFrpngu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFrpngu.jpg&h=554199b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaxJRHGLemy61DTAxhVKk6bDZWYDQ4TCGPJaLiHCeVfDB?filename=X2zuyn9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2zuyn9.jpg&h=63be1201&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n都係普通商場賣衫褲鞋襪, 唔多啱睇<br />\n5樓有個拉麵街, 但係夜晚已經鎖定咗食炸豬扒飯, 所以唔喺度食<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tabelog.com/fukuoka/A4001/A400103/40018942/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftabelog.com%2Ffukuoka%2FA4001%2FA400103%2F40018942%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RFQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=defce797\" target=\"_blank\">https://tabelog.com/fukuoka/A4001/A400103/40018942/</a><br />\n夜晚喺天神駅Solaria Stage嘅かつ心食, 而家Tabelog有 3.48分<br />\nSolaria Stage B2層全部都係食肆. 唔知係咪仲早(6點)所以唔太多人<br />\n<img src=\"https://tblg.k-img.com/restaurant/images/Rvw/82218/640x640_rect_82218242.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftblg.k-img.com%2Frestaurant%2Fimages%2FRvw%2F82218%2F640x640_rect_82218242.jpg&h=8d6df53e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖from tabelog<br />\n嗌咗個とんかつ膳(大)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVof2sSvRci9ycNTdZ14hUSeiiQmxThGfAjDzFDWSavSp?filename=9EsLReh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9EsLReh.jpg&h=d701dc28&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n炸得鬆脆又有汁, 幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食飽飽行多陣商場就返酒店<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>Day 1 完</strong></ins>"},{"pid":"23b0ee6b5fceac45e2bc4391f9c875aa29fbf403","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59f4c1a7d1380686d92ccc26b98b021c14d6f2fc","tid":2493724,"uid":292601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:38:42.000Z","msg":"正 我都係同你差唔多<br />\n2015左右獨遊北九州<br />\n自始愛上左呢個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但應該再無機會獨遊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:20:34.000Z","msg":"北九州夠靜又多地方行<br />\n<br />\n好掛住旅行嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd4535cc3f4b63928117cfe7063d01b93b40743","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:21:23.000Z","msg":"<del>北</del>九州夠靜又多地方行"},{"pid":"582442e66ebcc64e2992047bbd387f7c3974d110","tid":2493724,"uid":292601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:27:36.000Z","msg":"必食牛脷飯<br />\n仲可以去黑川 由布院浸溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd4ed9fefbfafff0c2c9945ecb50ce59b73e70f","tid":2493724,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:46:49.000Z","msg":"去過九洲如果唔係同屋企人一齊真係唔會想再去本洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2876f3ce7162b45fdad6320c0280aefbef48b5c0","tid":2493724,"uid":230702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:06:38.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你糸島自駕?"},{"pid":"b2daa6ecc5d6a54e7e5654740b4b80aea0a8b292","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:21:43.000Z","msg":"嗰時冇車牌<br />\n糸島咁多景點原本諗住踩單車KO哂佢，但中間有啲事，遲啲再講"},{"pid":"cb09584303dabb768c80337e2e7c783bc259aabe","tid":2493724,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59f4c1a7d1380686d92ccc26b98b021c14d6f2fc","tid":2493724,"uid":292601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:38:42.000Z","msg":"正 我都係同你差唔多<br />\n2015左右獨遊北九州<br />\n自始愛上左呢個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但應該再無機會獨遊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:28:47.000Z","msg":"我都好鍾意北九州獨遊左兩次<br />\n對上一次獨遊就係2018年跨年十日九州"},{"pid":"7ee28b66409a62e02d8bfaa96a5017508a04d594","tid":2493724,"uid":51738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:15:20.000Z","msg":"九州真係獨遊福地，人少，多景，多好嘢食<br />\n<br />\n好想再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39edbacb915b21d2a2a6f0522ae16cc80050738","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><ins><span class=\"x-large\">Day 2</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n由於買咗subway 2 day pass, 所以今日全日都會喺福岡巿內活動<br />\n今日鎖定咗食呢間ニクゼン 大名店, tabelog而家3.55分<br />\n<a href=\"https://tabelog.com/fukuoka/A4001/A400104/40030295/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftabelog.com%2Ffukuoka%2FA4001%2FA400104%2F40030295%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RFQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=83c53ecf\" target=\"_blank\">https://tabelog.com/fukuoka/A4001/A400104/40030295/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYHnPMXT4kpfYgkyqZTCJFJM4FBpjsfCrAHcbz4LTxaku?filename=fexHV4u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfexHV4u.jpg&h=5fd7ee8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n￥1200 有碗特盛燒牛丼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宣傳圖片啲牛好似成座山咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tblg.k-img.com/resize/660x370c/restaurant/images/Rvw/50496/50496231.jpg?token=7128bbd&amp;api=v2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftblg.k-img.com%2Fresize%2F660x370c%2Frestaurant%2Fimages%2FRvw%2F50496%2F50496231.jpg%3Ftoken%3D7128bbd%26api%3Dv2&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RFQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=d518bf0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tblg.k-img.com/resize/660x370c/restaurant/images/Rvw/50496/50496231.jpg?token=7128bbd&amp;api=v2</a><br />\n<br />\n由於11點半先開始營業, 所以首先去咗天神駅附近轉個圈<br />\n唔知點解每去一個地方, 我都鍾意去睇下啲政府建築物<br />\n呢日無例外, 去咗福岡巿役所, 不過冇乜特別, 正正常常一座大樓嘅樣<br />\n前面有個天神中央公園<br />\n再行去紅磚文化館<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ5o3a6appy9Mb95UzQa7rj974hQzL3pMXapxTzQk4qEu?filename=TKkFHNP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTKkFHNP.jpg&h=987ba9fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n睇得出都有啲歷史<br />\n對比起其他地方, 可以睇到香港喺保育文物/歷史建築方面真係唔掂<br />\n<br />\n行到差唔多就搭一個站地鐵去赤坂駅去餐廳<br />\n雖然已經預鬆咗時間大約11點去到餐廳, 但係門口已經有廿幾個人排緊隊 (好似都有好多韓國人?p.s. 由於福岡同南韓好近, 所以巿面上係會聽到好多寵寵寵)<br />\n等咗半個鐘到就慢慢放人入去<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWUkagMbWjZggH5kjcwZdjbAd1ke7TH35mcoSTRLW643V?filename=COX8RH2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCOX8RH2.jpg&h=450607ad&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n嗌咗個特盛燒牛丼, 跟一碗仔湯<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbzuZBmwXxcuNXPHSWESCGe6UKLsHmrJrzx2L7tVqhyZ7?filename=YkbBgaN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkbBgaN.jpg&h=3ba0ed70&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n嚟到同宣傳相差唔多, 都係成座山咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n味道中規中矩啦, 都有牛味, 不過佢係以量取勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食飽就去行大濠公園同福岡城跡"},{"pid":"06aaa03b47c02cf2fe74cea1dd91a9584f77ff7b","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T06:46:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span class=\"x-large\">Day 2 (cont.)</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n大濠公園距離食飯間餐廳得一個站<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP31ag311vVv2n3Ho4qEzJmYP3dWJNJMogNCJ5fdAQmBU?filename=0cAqT02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0cAqT02.jpg&h=801d82b0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n其實佢係一個好大嘅湖, 周圍由步行,緩跑徑同單車徑包住<br />\n公園入面有單車租, 另外又可以租鴨仔船喺湖度玩<br />\n雖然去嗰日係平日, 但都有唔少人<br />\n始終一個城巿入面有呢啲休憩地方好重要<br />\n工作忙碌完身心疲憊之後喺呢度沉澱一下心靈, 放鬆身心之後壓力都少啲<br />\n<br />\n橫掂啱啱食飽, 就慢慢沿住湖邊行一圈<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeJ5mZz51Jvg4AJ6k2FeKrqGorYvuuqPJnaV87CLUzNZi?filename=8Fq6DvD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Fq6DvD.jpg&h=16563d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CQvKqaE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCQvKqaE.jpg&h=b18a8571&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nbs8RQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnbs8RQE.jpg&h=049f37f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cAYPBhH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcAYPBhH.jpg&h=9bf9c6c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLRJFKp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLRJFKp.jpg&h=2f545902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfYcy4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfYcy4p.jpg&h=ccbf2d92&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AKKrDwZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAKKrDwZ.jpg&h=f3869253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1O2s7qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1O2s7qi.jpg&h=c41b3caa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R2d77qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2d77qi.jpg&h=7ca81f23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3Ky2YE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3Ky2YE.jpg&h=3d03ba8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0pqiuD9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0pqiuD9.jpg&h=d976bd4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行完一圈之後就去隔離嘅福岡城跡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SNva5es.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSNva5es.jpg&h=a963b18d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/prng0PE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fprng0PE.jpg&h=a629fd38&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKpGsuD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKpGsuD.jpg&h=7e895002&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijZfwWj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FijZfwWj.jpg&h=6e3998f2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFPy22Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFPy22Z.jpg&h=acd9888d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAPfwXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAPfwXL.jpg&h=fb827545&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lcn49Kq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLcn49Kq.jpg&h=7cc0463a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n福岡城跡唔算太多嘢睇, 其實佢似一個公園多啲, 保留住少少石建築同天守閣<br />\n不過其實福岡喺歷史上都有啲重要, 遣唐使就係經福岡&gt;博多灣出海<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HpqVwY7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHpqVwY7.jpg&h=f722c8cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7va5i8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7va5i8.jpg&h=4c796a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後去福岡塔睇日落<br />\n嗰時秋天尾, 5點幾就天黑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BLrp9MN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBLrp9MN.jpg&h=63217f31&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qX3PBrN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqX3PBrN.jpg&h=1253d736&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vREy26M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvREy26M.jpg&h=80df5ee6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sf7s7Aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsf7s7Aa.jpg&h=3550e29c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QKiczfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQKiczfa.jpg&h=1b605bc1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GxZvkU9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGxZvkU9.jpg&h=daa6df35&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQNHWtv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQNHWtv.jpg&h=da23b850&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oArJFVa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoArJFVa.jpg&h=9dd77617&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqRp9OM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqRp9OM.jpg&h=1ce0fe3c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Cs1sAr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Cs1sAr.jpg&h=e3f29495&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食碗拉麵就返酒店 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LsWJFXG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLsWJFXG.jpg&h=3cbe6fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y0zrDJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY0zrDJQ.jpg&h=f6c83296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span class=\"x-large\">Day 2 完</span></ins></strong>"},{"pid":"5935bb712d66cd41ba9ca787fc5364f4c154104f","tid":2493724,"uid":230702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T07:42:44.000Z","msg":"你喺福岡城搭咩去福岡塔?"},{"pid":"0da0cb14a10d78a14f944cdfb26a60afc31c33ce","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5935bb712d66cd41ba9ca787fc5364f4c154104f","tid":2493724,"uid":230702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T07:42:44.000Z","msg":"你喺福岡城搭咩去福岡塔?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T08:47:46.000Z","msg":"既然問到, 就講多少少啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ZrxzRy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ZrxzRy.png&h=4e01d639&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買得subway pass當然要用盡佢<br />\n行完福岡城跡(即係上圖黑圈)之後, 大約3點45分, 拿拿聲去福岡塔先, 因為日本秋冬好早日落, 遲咗上去如果日已落咪晒咗入場費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行去上圖右面少少嘅赤坂駅搭鐵去西新駅<br />\n西新駅已經係距離福岡塔最近嘅地鐵站, 不過其實都有一段距離, 慢慢行過去大約半個鐘<br />\n途中會經過西南學院大學, 另外有高中,小學<br />\n啱啱撞正JD JK放學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(不過無圖)<br />\n<br />\n再行前少少經過福岡巿博物館<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QmpLauo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQmpLauo.jpg&h=d3a7750c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2UfxHK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2UfxHK.jpg&h=98c7464e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tP0a52J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtP0a52J.jpg&h=1cc4bf06&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n不過今日行程重點唔喺度, 而且之後會去太宰府嘅九州國立博物館, 所以就唔入呢間喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dj5qUWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDj5qUWY.jpg&h=89463533&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n圓形嗰座係福岡巨蛋<br />\n<br />\n見仲未咁快日落, 就行下福岡塔前面嘅海濱公園<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MvzrEpy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMvzrEpy.jpg&h=eaf09706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FdMqawe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFdMqawe.jpg&h=8103ecf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n差唔多時間就上去福岡塔lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Day 2補充完</ins></strong>"},{"pid":"b297086b365ac588755f496b524e8c9873213a28","tid":2493724,"uid":8388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T12:32:57.000Z","msg":"博多駅牛腸鍋世一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d3eb073c6d611006dfd2cae4a2cccf2289a165","tid":2493724,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"留名睇遊記"},{"pid":"3a7dd52c9b568448c898609dd2f2bb6ab66ac86e","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T06:18:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span class=\"x-large\">Day 3</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n上面介紹話Day 3去太宰府, 但其實呢日係去糸島先啱, Day 4先去太宰府<br />\n<br />\n其實plan行程嘅時候都有諗雖然大部分人去北九州會去埋別府、由布院、阿蘇嗰邊, 但係我今次就唔想去咁遠, 始終搭車來回都冇咗大半日, 如果去嗰邊住又要搬行李<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我就揾究竟福岡周邊有邊啲地方好去而又夠近, 最尾揾咗糸島呢個地方. 不過網上關於糸島嘅介紹唔係咁多, 咁啱又畀我見到呢個blog<br />\n<a href=\"https://77ig77.blogspot.com/2016/06/2016-5-23.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F77ig77.blogspot.com%2F2016%2F06%2F2016-5-23.html&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RFQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=d2a6c0c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://77ig77.blogspot.com/2016/06/2016-5-23.html</a><br />\n佢哋正正就係踩單車去糸島, 桜井二見ヶ浦又好似幾靚, 所以最後就決定踩單車去糸島<br />\n<br />\n糸島喺福岡天神西邊廿幾公里, 即日來回計過應該OK<br />\n單車公司方面揾到有間Seaside Bike, 見佢有個station喺酒店附近, 1000円就可以租一日, 於是諗住食完早餐就去租單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講起連鎖食堂, 我諗好多人都會諗起松屋、すき家、なか卯等等<br />\n而喺酒店對面轉個靚彎就有一間やよい軒, 於是呢日早餐就喺呢度解決<br />\n9點幾去到, 唔知點解冇乜人<br />\n叫咗個親子丼大盛750円<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sPicGYK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsPicGYK.jpg&h=609786d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n(手震濛咗)<br />\n都幾大碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食飽飽就行過去單車station諗住租單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原本我以為佢係一間舖頭, 因為google map show 到係一間單車舖, 但去到問個老細, 佢就嘰哩咕嚕 灑手擰頭咁, 指我出去再指住前面. 咁我嗰時唔識日文, 不過都估佢係話個station喺指嗰個方向,  所以就向嗰邊行<br />\n行咗一兩個路口, 見到個老細追上嚟, 再指住對面馬路嗰堆單車畀我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢一刻我真係感受到日本人嘅服務態度竟然可以咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\narigodo完之後就發現原來啲單車係好似Locobike咁樣擺喺路邊, 另外有個架鎖住啲轆<br />\n見介紹要download佢個app, download完先發現原來要日本電話/email先登記到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最尾搞咗一輪都係唔得, 即刻灰哂, 心諗唔通今日單車之旅要取消?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前research 嗰時都睇過其實糸島都有單車租, 不過數量比較少<br />\n就諗住搏一搏, 過去嗰邊先睇下仲有冇得租<br />\n於是就搭JR過去糸島嘅筑前前原駅<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>待續</strong></ins>"},{"pid":"f143d4d812ed57ee183b972bb31be1898501b8b1","tid":2493724,"uid":4850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T06:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e3d20705ab8d521775497d373049e68039347f","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T07:50:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span class=\"x-large\">Day 3 (cont.)</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n糸島巿觀光協會就喺筑前前原駅出站嘅右手邊<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.itoshima-kanko.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/rental_bicycle_top.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.itoshima-kanko.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2Frental_bicycle_top.jpg&h=8dd2c43c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.itoshima-kanko.net/rental-bicycle/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.itoshima-kanko.net%2Frental-bicycle%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RFQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=16347ab9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.itoshima-kanko.net/rental-bicycle/</a><br />\n佢有兩種單車租, 一種係電動嘅, 有10部, 另一種係普通單車得4部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好彩去到仲有普通單車剩,可以租<br />\n嗰時另外仲有兩個人租嗰種電動嘅<br />\n唔記得嗰時租要幾錢, 而家睇返網頁就要&yen;1500 8個鐘<br />\n畀Passport登記畀埋錢, 佢再試打你提供嘅電話號碼, 成功就試車出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PRP3OUi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPRP3OUi.jpg&h=0e4069ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YZhg8Ui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYZhg8Ui.jpg&h=34c2357a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞完手續都12點幾, 佢要5點前還車所以就唔去咁多景點喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oqxAE3e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoqxAE3e.png&h=57ac8d11&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n1 船越漁港-&gt; 2 岐志漁港 -&gt; 3 芥屋の大門 -&gt; 4 桜井二見ヶ浦 -&gt; 5  一蘭の森<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kXMRdrn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXMRdrn.jpg&h=88f4cb2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngt4yrn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fngt4yrn.jpg&h=cfefc7ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OKPZ6Mn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOKPZ6Mn.jpg&h=31eca2dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2pWpx2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2pWpx2.jpg&h=503d5e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QDMqhS2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQDMqhS2.jpg&h=4de93314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能大部分人識得糸島係因為食蠔, 兩個漁港都有一排蠔小屋, 入去食嘅話要著店舖提供嘅好似雨褸嘅一件袍, 類似咁樣, 每間舖都唔同色, 門口睇都幾搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/bajenny/1516614435-4206244217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fbajenny%2F1516614435-4206244217.jpg&h=212e8a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(上圖取自網上)<br />\n呢次去我冇入到去食, 因為得一條友, 不過之後都有啲後悔, 其實一個人燒蠔又有咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過蠔屋之後繼續踩去芥屋の大門<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.itoshima-kanko.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/keya_no_oto1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.itoshima-kanko.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fkeya_no_oto1.jpg&h=7d480aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(上圖取自網上)<br />\n上網睇呢個洞其實係因為岩石經過連年海水侵蝕而形成, 不過踩到去發現原來要搭船出海先睇到呢個角度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjJcHqx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjJcHqx.jpg&h=0ac3f66b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後面睇過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n桜井二見ヶ浦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8qMt0d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8qMt0d3.jpg&h=285ada3a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mbNUbkH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmbNUbkH.jpg&h=21d1235b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wDRmANm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDRmANm.jpg&h=c0ee48ad&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8238fNo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8238fNo.jpg&h=9868e626&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n嗰兩嚿石又叫夫婦岩, 應該係糸島最多遊客嘅地方<br />\n如果較啱季節日落時間嚟到, 會見到太陽慢慢喺兩嚿石中間降落直至消失喺地平線, 都幾靚<br />\n不過一個人冇乜好做, 影咗幾張相就走了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後踩去一蘭食嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢間一蘭の森店係日本唯一一間工場併設店舖<br />\n根據官網介紹, 「現做超生麵」做好之後即刻喺店舖提供, 所以會比一般拉麵有更多水份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mMwebq2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmMwebq2.jpg&h=104bbfa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Add0Rq1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdd0Rq1.jpg&h=5722dcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0WE6Zk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0WE6Zk.jpg&h=6e9dcc24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kro8fSG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkro8fSG.jpg&h=30e25283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n差唔多夠鐘還車, 所以食完睇咗一陣就拿拿臨踩返去筑前前原駅還車之後搭車返福岡巿區<br />\n由於都踩咗幾個鐘單車, 來回一蘭又多上山路段<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 所以返去酒店之後都抖咗一陣<br />\n<a href=\"https://tabelog.com/fukuoka/A4001/A400103/40043101/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftabelog.com%2Ffukuoka%2FA4001%2FA400103%2F40043101%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RFQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=2b3fb4c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tabelog.com/fukuoka/A4001/A400103/40043101/</a><br />\n之後去呢間稲田屋Sun食豚丼, <br />\n呢間嘢居酒屋格局, 有個客坐喺吧枱係咁同老闆吹水, 我又唔識日文都係安心食飯算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3N7wX9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3N7wX9b.jpg&h=c855c7a4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c5h5h9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc5h5h9b.jpg&h=1a5b2875&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n豬肉燒得幾香, 跟住佢幾種方法食之後都係最鍾意原味撈埋隻蛋就咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完就返酒店繼續訓<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span class=\"x-large\">Day 3完</span></ins></strong>"},{"pid":"1e272843a5aa1b59535b1f4bb946c09312dc8025","tid":2493724,"uid":4253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:58:38.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd108762a4fbc55c0986d63049f01009713c48c","tid":2493724,"uid":189015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:53:53.000Z","msg":"糸島睇落幾舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似少見有po係踩單車去<br />\n芥屋大門個海邊似乎都幾靚"},{"pid":"829606e3694ef2c42e95d60bf6be405d79f93e36","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cd108762a4fbc55c0986d63049f01009713c48c","tid":2493724,"uid":189015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:53:53.000Z","msg":"糸島睇落幾舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似少見有po係踩單車去<br />\n芥屋大門個海邊似乎都幾靚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T13:27:19.000Z","msg":"去糸島嘅人應該多數都係自駕<br />\n沿住海邊可以暫時遠離煩囂，係舒服嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}